Class SignalListenerContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • framework.communication.internal.signal.SignalListenerContainer

  • public class SignalListenerContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    Container class used for holding signal names to signal listener relationships This container is usually used when keeping track of which signals are attached to a particular entity
